# Force LF line endings for all text files on every platform.
# Without this, Windows checkouts apply core.autocrlf=true which
# breaks snapshot byte-for-byte comparison and a markdown regex
# in __test__/diagnostic-codes-drift.spec.ts that hard-codes \n.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary artifacts — never normalize.
*.node binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
